<PageTitle>Home - Music Streaming App</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to Music Streaming App</h1>

<p>
    This application allows you to upload and stream music files with real-time integration
    using SignalR. You can see what music is playing on other connected devices in real-time.
</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Features</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li>Upload music files (MP3, WAV, OGG formats)</li>
                    <li>Stream music from the server</li>
                    <li>See what's playing on other connected devices</li>
                    <li>Real-time updates using SignalR</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
